dct_description_sm: Map shows international boundaries, railways, oil fields, historical monuments. Locates major oases, and Qattara depression. On verso: tourist information, distance chart, and tables of mean air temperatures. "With the compliments of the Ministry of Tourism, Egypt 1970." Includes location map. Lower left margin: "K. Kamel. 1969." Landmarks shown pictorially. Shows boundaries, towns, capitals, cultivated land, bathing places, railways, oilfields, and palms. Tourist information and tables, in English and Arabic, on verso. "K. Kamel. 1969"
